          "icon": "🪄",
          "iconColor": "bg-purple-500",
          "agentName": "图片编辑优化师",
          "agentTaskType": "image-edit",
          "agentReferenceImageUrl": "{{input-image-img-edit-parallel.output.imageUrl}}",
          "agentNumberOfImages": 1,
          "inputMapping": "{{agent-edit-plan.output.text}}\\n\\n请严格执行主图要求：纯白背景，无文字无水印，保留产品主体细节。仅返回编辑后的图片。",
          "instructions": "执行 image-chat-edit，重点保证主体一致与主图合规。"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "tool-scene-edit",
        "type": "agent",
        "position": {
          "x": 1240,
          "y": 240
        },
        "data": {
          "type": "agent",
          "label": "场景图图生图",
          "description": "场景智能体执行图生图",
          "icon": "🏞️",
          "iconColor": "bg-indigo-500",
          "agentName": "图片编辑优化师",
          "agentTaskType": "image-edit",
          "agentReferenceImageUrl": "{{input-image-img-edit-parallel.output.imageUrl}}",
          "agentNumberOfImages": 1,
          "inputMapping": "{{agent-edit-plan.output.text}}\\n\\n请严格执行场景图要求：保持产品主体一致，增强使用场景真实感。仅返回编辑后的图片。",
          "instructions": "执行 image-chat-edit，保持产品形态不变并增强场景叙事。"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "tool-detail-edit",
        "type": "agent",
        "position": {
          "x": 1240,
          "y": 380
        },
        "data": {
          "type": "agent",
          "label": "卖点图图生图",
          "description": "卖点智能体执行图生图",
          "icon": "🔍",
          "iconColor": "bg-violet-500",
          "agentName": "图片编辑优化师",
          "agentTaskType": "image-edit",
          "agentReferenceImageUrl": "{{input-image-img-edit-parallel.output.imageUrl}}",
          "agentNumberOfImages": 1,
          "inputMapping": "{{agent-edit-plan.output.text}}\\n\\n请严格执行卖点图要求：突出材质与工艺细节，背景简洁。仅返回编辑后的图片。",
          "instructions": "执行 image-chat-edit，优先强化材质纹理和细节层次。"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "merge-img-edit",
        "type": "merge",
        "position": {
          "x": 1480,
          "y": 240
        },
        "data": {
          "type": "merge",
          "label": "编辑汇总",
          "description": "汇总并行图生图结果",
          "icon": "🔗",
          "iconColor": "bg-gray-500",
          "mergeStrategy": "append"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "agent-edit-qa",
        "type": "agent",
        "position": {
          "x": 1720,
          "y": 240
        },
        "data": {
          "type": "agent",
          "label": "结果质检",
          "description": "输出最终可交付图清单与复修建议",
          "icon": "✅",
          "iconColor": "bg-emerald-500",
          "agentName": "图片编辑优化师",
          "inputMapping": "并行图生图结果摘要：{{merge-img-edit.output.text}}\\n编辑规划：{{agent-edit-plan.output.text}}",
          "instructions": "请对已生成图生图结果做交付质检（不要再索要输入）：\n1. 每类图选择最优结果（主图/场景图/卖点图）\n2. 标注不合规风险（主图规范、清晰度、一致性）\n3. 输出可直接交付与需二次编辑清单\n4. 给出下一轮编辑提示词（如需要）"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "end-img-edit-parallel",
        "type": "end",
        "position": {
          "x": 1960,
          "y": 240
        },
        "data": {
          "type": "end",
          "label": "图生图结果",
          "description": "输出并行图生图交付结果",
          "icon": "🏁",
          "iconColor": "bg-green-500"
        }
      }
